o the Devil’s Sinkhole, where this world and the next come together, bringing Papa and Calley, Pelo Blanco and Arlon to a climax that will leave readers clamoring for the next adventure.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Okt 2021) 0aFamilieszTexasvFiction. 0aFamilies--Texas--Fiction. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aCiardiello, Joe.40uhttps://doi.org/10.7560/30974240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781477309759423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781477309759/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK